Class Length

  • java.lang.Object
    • Length

  • class Length
extends java.lang.Object
    Class Length retains information about limits concerning numbers of signs which can sit in character string inputting by user during creating new customer, item, order or quantity. Most limits correspond with data in ERD diagram of database. One of them concerning max value of int data type.
    Version:
    2.0 15.03.2018
    Author:
    Magdalena Wisniewska
